      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

      *@1  신용공여자기자본기본정보조회
           PERFORM S3100-QJL0391-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3100-QJL0391-CALL-EXT

      *@1  거액익스포져(LEX)총액조회
           PERFORM S3200-QJL4054-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3200-QJL4054-CALL-EXT

      *@1  전영업년월일 익스포져 조회
           PERFORM S3300-QJL4054-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3300-QJL4054-CALL-EXT

