           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 신용공여자기자본기본정보조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJL0391-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0391-IN

      *@1.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL0391-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월
           MOVE XDJL4054-I-INQURY-BASE-DD(1:6)
             TO XQJL0391-I-BASE-YM

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL0391 XQJL0391-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   기준년월
           MOVE XQJL0391-O-BASE-YM
             TO XDJL4054-O-BASC-CAPTL-BASE-YM

      *@   은행기본자본 ( 보통주자본 + 기타자본 )
           COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL
                = XQJL0391-O-OSHR-CAPTL +
                  XQJL0391-O-ETC-CAPTL

           COMPUTE WK-BNK-BASC-CAPTL
                = XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL / 100000000

      *@   한도규제(기본자본x25%)
           COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-LIMT-REGUL1
                = WK-BNK-BASC-CAPTL * 0.25

      *@   한도규제(기본자본x20%)
           COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-LIMT-REGUL2
                = WK-BNK-BASC-CAPTL * 0.2
           .
       S3100-QJL0391-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 거액익스포져(LEX)총액조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3200-QJL4054-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL4054-IN

      *@1.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL4054-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4054-I-INQURY-BASE-DD
             TO XQJL4054-I-BASE-YMD

      *@   차주고객식별자
           MOVE '%%%%%%%%%%'
             TO XQJL4054-I-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL4054 XQJL4054-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   출력건수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL4054-O-PRSNT-NOITM1

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4054-O-PRSNT-NOITM1

      *@       순서
               MOVE XQJL4054-O-RANKG(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4054-O-RANKG(WK-I)

      *@       차주고객식별자
               MOVE XQJL4054-O-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4054-O-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)

      *@       단일거래상대방
               MOVE XQJL4054-O-DBTRZ-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4054-O-UNY-TRAN-CNPRT(WK-I)

      *@       단일거래상대방구분
               IF XQJL4054-O-BSM-T-CNPRT-DSTCD(WK-I) = '1'
                 MOVE '단일거래상대방'
                   TO XDJL4054-O-BSM-T-CNPRT-DSTCD(WK-I)
               ELSE
                 MOVE '거래상대방그룹'
                   TO XDJL4054-O-BSM-T-CNPRT-DSTCD(WK-I)
               END-IF

      *@       총익스포져
               MOVE XQJL4054-O-BSM-CCF-AUC(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR(WK-I)

      *@       거액익스포져비율(총익스포져/은행기본자본)
               IF XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL > 0

                   COMPUTE WK-RND-RATO
                        =  XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR(WK-I)
                           / XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL

                   COMPUTE WK-BSM-EXPSR-RATO ROUNDED
                        =  WK-RND-RATO * CO-NUM-100

                   MOVE WK-BSM-EXPSR-RATO
                     TO XDJL4054-O-BSM-EXPSR-RATO(WK-I)
               ELSE
                   MOVE 0
                     TO XDJL4054-O-BSM-EXPSR-RATO(WK-I)
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3200-QJL4054-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  전영업년월일을 구한다.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3210-CJIDT16-CALL-RTN.

      *@    초기화
           INITIALIZE XCJIDT16-IN
      *@    호출변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD         TO XCJIDT16-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4054-I-INQURY-BASE-DD TO XCJIDT16-I-YMD
      *@   구분코드
           MOVE CO-CHA-1                  TO XCJIDT16-I-DSTCD
      *@   공통 UTILITY CALL
           #DYCALL CJIDT16 YCCOMMON-CA XCJIDT16-CA
      *@    호출결과　확인
           IF XCJIDT16-R-STAT = ZEROS
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XCJIDT16-R-ERRCD
                     XCJIDT16-R-TREAT-CD
                     XCJIDT16-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3210-CJIDT16-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  전영업년월일 익스포져 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-QJL4054-CALL-RTN.

      *@   전영업년월일구하기
           PERFORM S3210-CJIDT16-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3210-CJIDT16-CALL-EXT

      *    신용공여자기자본기본정보조회(전영업일)
           PERFORM S3400-QJL0391-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3400-QJL0391-CALL-EXT

           PERFORM VARYING WK-J FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-J > XDJL4054-O-PRSNT-NOITM1

               INITIALIZE XQJL4054-IN

      *@       입력값조립
      *@       그룹회사코드
               MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
                 TO XQJL4054-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@       기준년월일(전영업일)
               MOVE XCJIDT16-O-BF-BZOPR-YMD
                 TO XQJL4054-I-BASE-YMD

      *@       차주고객식별자
               MOVE XDJL4054-O-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR(WK-J)
                 TO XQJL4054-I-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR

      *@       프로그램　호출
               #DYSQLA QJL4054 XQJL4054-CA

      *@       호출결과　확인
               EVALUATE TRUE
                   WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                   WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                        CONTINUE
                   WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                        #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
               END-EVALUATE

      *        총익스포져(전영업일)
               MOVE XQJL4054-O-BSM-CCF-AUC(1)
                 TO WK-BF-TOTAL-EXPSR

      *@       총익스포져변동
               COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR-FLXBL(WK-J)
                    =  (XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR(WK-J)
                         - WK-BF-TOTAL-EXPSR) / 100000000

               IF WK-BF-BNK-BASC-CAPTL > 0
      *            거액익스포져비율(전영업일)
                   COMPUTE WK-RND-RATO
                        =  (WK-BF-TOTAL-EXPSR
                           / WK-BF-BNK-BASC-CAPTL)

                   COMPUTE WK-BF-BSM-EXPSR-RATO ROUNDED
                        =  WK-RND-RATO * CO-NUM-100

               ELSE
                   MOVE 0
                     TO WK-BF-BSM-EXPSR-RATO
               END-IF

      *@       거액익스포져비율변동
               COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-BSM-E-RATO-FLXBL(WK-J)
                    =  XDJL4054-O-BSM-EXPSR-RATO(WK-J)
                        - WK-BF-BSM-EXPSR-RATO

           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3300-QJL4054-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 신용공여자기자본기본정보조회(전영업일)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3400-QJL0391-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0391-IN

      *@1.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL0391-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월
           MOVE XCJIDT16-O-BF-BZOPR-YMD(1:6)
             TO XQJL0391-I-BASE-YM

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL0391 XQJL0391-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   은행기본자본 ( 보통주자본 + 기타자본 )
           COMPUTE WK-BF-BNK-BASC-CAPTL
                = XQJL0391-O-OSHR-CAPTL +
                  XQJL0391-O-ETC-CAPTL
           .
       S3400-QJL0391-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 출력값 세팅
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3500-OUTPUT-RTN.
      *   은행기본자본
           COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL
                = XDJL4054-O-BNK-BASC-CAPTL / 100000000

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4054-O-PRSNT-NOITM1

      *@       총익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR(WK-I)
                    =  XDJL4054-O-TOTAL-EXPSR(WK-I) / 100000000

           END-PERFORM

            .
       S3500-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  처리종료
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S9000-FINAL-RTN.
      *@정상종료
           #OKEXIT  CO-STAT-OK
           .
       S9000-FINAL-EXT.
           EXIT.
